
flowchart TD
    User[User] -->|Submit Business Idea| IdeaAgent[Idea Understanding Agent]
    
    IdeaAgent -->|User Input| NormalVal[Normal Validation]
    NormalVal -->|Check Fields| LLMVal[LLM Validation Agent]
    LLMVal -->|Evaluate: Clarity, Actionability, Uniqueness| StructJSON[Structured JSON Output with Score]
    StructJSON --> DecisionEngine{Decision Engine}
    
    DecisionEngine -->|Score < 50| Clarify[Ask Clarification]
    Clarify -->|Resubmit| IdeaAgent
    
    DecisionEngine -->|Score 50-80| CollectMore[Collect More Details]
    CollectMore -->|Proceed| BizCollection[Business Information Collection]
    
    DecisionEngine -->|Score > 80| BizCollection
    
    BizCollection -->|AI-Guided Questionnaire| Questions["Location, Budget, Target Customers<br/>Business Type, Experience Level<br/>Goal Type, Core Painpoint<br/>Launch Timeline"]
    Questions --> PlanningLayer[AI Agent Planning Layer]
    
    PlanningLayer --> StartupMgr[Startup Manager Agent<br/>Agent Orchestrator]
    StartupMgr -->|Distribute Tasks| AgentPool[Specialized AI Agents Pool]
    
    AgentPool --> Market[Market Research Agent]
    AgentPool --> Finance[Finance Agent]
    AgentPool --> Brand[Brand Agent]
    AgentPool --> Website[Website/Product Agent]
    AgentPool --> Marketing[Marketing Agent]
    
    Market -->|Competitor Analysis<br/>Customer Trends<br/>Market Size| MarketOut[Market Intelligence]
    Finance -->|Cost Estimation<br/>Revenue Prediction<br/>Break-even Analysis| FinanceOut[Financial Model]
    Brand -->|Brand Identity<br/>Name Suggestions<br/>Logo & Palette| BrandOut[Brand Package]
    Website -->|Landing Page Design<br/>Feature Suggestions<br/>Prototype| WebOut[Digital Presence]
    Marketing -->|Social Strategy<br/>Customer Acquisition<br/>90-day Roadmap| MarketingOut[Growth Plan]
    
    MarketOut --> FatalCheck{Fatal Flaw<br/>Detection?}
    FinanceOut --> FatalCheck
    BrandOut --> FatalCheck
    WebOut --> FatalCheck
    MarketingOut --> FatalCheck
    
    FatalCheck -->|Critical Issue| Pivot[Signal to Startup Manager<br/>Pause/Pivot Workflow]
    Pivot -->|Reassess| StartupMgr
    
    FatalCheck -->|No Issues| Persistence[Persistence & Versioning Layer<br/>Decision Log + Real-Time Data<br/>Tavily Search API Integration]
    
    Persistence --> Dashboard[Startup Blueprint Dashboard]
    Dashboard -->|Render Output| InteractiveRef[Interactive Refinement Phase]
    
    InteractiveRef -->|User Command| RefinementLogic{User Requests<br/>Changes?}
    RefinementLogic -->|Make it Cheaper| UpdateBudget[Update Cost Model]
    RefinementLogic -->|Target New Segment| UpdatePersona[Update Customer Persona]
    RefinementLogic -->|Other Changes| UpdateGeneral[Update Relevant Sections]
    
    UpdateBudget --> VersionControl[Version Control & Context Management]
    UpdatePersona --> VersionControl
    UpdateGeneral --> VersionControl
    
    VersionControl -->|Apply Changes| Dashboard
    VersionControl -->|Or Rollback| Dashboard
    
    Dashboard -->|Ready to Export| FinalBlueprint[Final Startup Blueprint]
    FinalBlueprint -->|Markdown/HTML/CSS| Output1[Beautiful Interactive Dashboard]
    FinalBlueprint -->|Export to PDF| Output2[Investor-Ready PDF]
    
    Output1 --> End["✓ Business Overview<br/>✓ Market Intelligence<br/>✓ Financial Model<br/>✓ Brand Package<br/>✓ Digital Presence<br/>✓ Growth Plan"]
    Output2 --> End
    
    classDef userNode stroke:#f87171,fill:#fef2f2
    classDef validationNode stroke:#a78bfa,fill:#f5f3ff
    classDef collectionNode stroke:#38bdf8,fill:#f0f9ff
    classDef agentNode stroke:#4ade80,fill:#f0fdf4
    classDef outputNode stroke:#facc15,fill:#fefce8
    classDef decisionNode stroke:#fb923c,fill:#fff7ed
    
    class User userNode
    class IdeaAgent,NormalVal,LLMVal,StructJSON validationNode
    class BizCollection,Questions collectionNode
    class PlanningLayer,StartupMgr,Market,Finance,Brand,Website,Marketing agentNode
    class Dashboard,FinalBlueprint,Output1,Output2,End outputNode
    class DecisionEngine,FatalCheck,RefinementLogic decisionNode